title: Minan, Zanjan
text: Minan (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Mīnān) is a village in <a href="Qanibeyglu%20Rural%20District">Qanibeyglu Rural District</a>, <a href="Zanjanrud%20District">Zanjanrud District</a>, <a href="Zanjan%20County">Zanjan County</a>, <a href="Zanjan%20Province">Zanjan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 139, in 29 families.
